title: The Tudors - Season 1 - Opening Intro
author: GotPilot
comment:
Honestly, they couldn't have picked a better actress to play Anne! Natalie Dormer is so beautiful and mysterious. Plus Maria Doyle was absolutely perfect in her role as Catherine, so graceful.
Love this series too much!
I think this is the most 2000s intro ever. There is no better intro than this.
Love the smug look on the Cardinal's face as he shuffles the coins
Natalie Dormer 😍 Just as beautiful as this ethereal tune.
